                <li><strong>Java:</strong> The entire functionality of the app is done through Java. 
                  I made use of Java's objected oriented nature to organize data into appropriate classes.</li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Firebase:</strong> The saving and retrieval of matches, the user accounts, and any other online feature rely on Firebase Storage.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Android Studio:</strong> I used Android Studio to develop the java and xml files used by this app.</li>
              </ul>
